          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800"><td class="py-2 pr-4">p_k = b_(k+1)</td><td class="pr-4 text-green-300">(list-ref sorted (+ i 1))</td><td class="font-sans">Per-click payment = next bid</td></tr>
