    <div class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-400 mt-10">
      Ready for the real thing? <a href="https://www.aeaweb.org/articles?id=10.1257/aer.97.1.242">Read the paper</a>.
    </div>

